org.smartfrog
Class SFParse

java.lang.Object
  org.smartfrog.SFParse
All Implemented Interfaces:
MessageKeys
public final class SFParse
extends java.lang.Object
implements MessageKeys

SFParse provides the utility methods to parse file descriptions and generate the parsing report. The main function looks for a filename(s) on the argument line and parses locally.

The main loop of SFParse reads an optionset. It then parses the file(s) and/or prints the status report depending on the options.

Warning This class is not thread safe; the static methods used shared static data structures. It is intended to be executed in from Main() methods and not from Java code.
